# Commit and Deploy After Every Prompt

After making any code changes in response to the user, always:

1. **Commit** the changes with a descriptive message
2. **Deploy to Vercel** by running `npx vercel --prod` from the project root

The site is live at https://girlsgone.digital. Deploying ensures changes go live immediately.

GitHub push may fail if the repo is not yet created; Vercel deploy will still work.
